header  : build two switches and verify ipsec vxlan output connectivity
topology: sw1 100.100.0.241 <==== IPSec ====> sw2 100.100.0.242 | svc 192.56.0.1 <---- VxLAN output - svc 192.56.0.2
topology: # Topology:
